  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of <strong>Coral</strong>, one of the last survivors of a failed mission to colonize an unknown planet, and explore what remains of the mothership, the <strong>Crystal Mountain</strong>, now a derelict wreck shrouded in flickering lights, metallic echoes, and unsettling sounds. But you're not alone: alien creatures, oozing black masses with a single red eye, roam the ruins.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No explicit missions, no arrows pointing the way. Your curiosity is your guide: explore freely and follow the hidden clues scattered throughout the world. You'll need to piece together traces and fragments of the past to uncover the truth. Nothing is as it seems, each discovery may reveal unexpected connections and unlock secrets waiting to be found.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Non-linear exploration of vertically interconnected areas<br></li><li> Fast-paced, dynamic combat system<br></li><li> RPG elements with unlockable abilities and upgrades<br></li><li> Intense and memorable boss fights<br></li><li> Tons of secrets to discover</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/69065362ff9fca58de37340ed03c9980.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of <strong>Coral</strong>, one of the last survivors of a failed mission to colonize an unknown planet, and explore what remains of the mothership, the <strong>Crystal Mountain</strong>, now a derelict wreck shrouded in flickering lights, metallic echoes, and unsettling sounds. But you're not alone: alien creatures, oozing black masses with a single red eye, roam the ruins.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/fe38397347e39b5176bdaffa38d49c5a.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No explicit missions, no arrows pointing the way. Your curiosity is your guide: explore freely and follow the hidden clues scattered throughout the world. You'll need to piece together traces and fragments of the past to uncover the truth. Nothing is as it seems, each discovery may reveal unexpected connections and unlock secrets waiting to be found.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/e38d141b86f7f3c0b07f2bc7793fb897.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Non-linear exploration of vertically interconnected areas<br></li><li> Fast-paced, dynamic combat system<br></li><li> RPG elements with unlockable abilities and upgrades<br></li><li> Intense and memorable boss fights<br></li><li> Tons of secrets to discover</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.poster.avif?t=1747034568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.webm?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/2c6f4bafe08d662efa6010bdfafbfc4c.mp4?t=1747034568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
